Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之環嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被菲莉雅湧出的力量解放了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深淵的祭壇一定就在那裡哞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 一起去深淵的祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:38.61,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,650)\blur5\pos(322.267,1059.734)}{\1cBCE347}路{\1cFFFFFF}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:11.61,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}眩しい光が土を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:17.36,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　そのたねは十分に芽を伸ばせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:28.12,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}冷たい雨にも　強い風にも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:32.53,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何者でも揺るがない魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:36.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕らの背を押すわけはなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:40.63,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　くじけそうになった日もあっただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:44.42,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不思議な力あふれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:51.15,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愛の指す方へ　駆け出す少年のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.97,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}長い冬越え　僕ら包む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:02:00.34,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春の息吹　福音になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.74,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕は君を探し求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:09.19,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}この日をずっと待ち続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:13.54,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}信じることの強さをそれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:17.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}それはいつかの孤独を癒すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:24.00,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あぁ　もしも君が星に帰れと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:29.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}新しいたねをまこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:11.61,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}耀眼的光芒照亮大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:17.36,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}含苞之種由此茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:28.12,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論是冰冷的雨水  還是強勁的烈風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:32.53,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這是誰都無法動搖的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:36.91,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}助我們一臂之力的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:40.63,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}曾經也有灰心喪氣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:44.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不可思議的力量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:51.15,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}朝著愛的方向奔跑吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}跨越長冬  將我們包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:02:00.34,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春天的氣息  成為福音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.74,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:09.19,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一直等待今天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:13.54,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}堅信著信任這一強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:17.95,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不久它便會治癒你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:24.00,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果你將回歸繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:29.03,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}去播撒新的種子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣才能到那裡去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼好辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許可以使用水路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這條河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該一直延伸到那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 該怎麼過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R7駕駛艙體積大 可以浮在水上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做個木筏的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就可以過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分工台作 一起收集做木筏的材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧托！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多應該沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要補充點營養呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘑…蘑菇真的不行哞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 我查過品種了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不要就是不要哞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這濃郁辛辣的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:03:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:03:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圓…圓筒鍋哞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林裡的…咖哩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太可疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 感覺這味道有點熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 這我的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓你們高興高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行配件比預想的來得早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的戰鬥要是有它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以給那東西致命一擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 有什麼新情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是一直在聯繋蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這香味和熟透的帕裡米亞果實很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過下火就可以吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天城博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始要讓你負青這個人物的護衛以及監視任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經聽上面說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這真得動用軍隊的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人提出了利瑪假說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是宇宙飛來物質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以帶來超過吉夫特礦的能源的假說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為這種天方夜譚就花上這麼大規模的預算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是天方夜譚也好 異端邪說也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不能棄之不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它可以將這顆星球引導向真正的頂峰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧 無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就只需要按照命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把妨礙你們的敵人除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 寶貝 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我好好看會顯微鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在忙的話我們就下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您讀了我的論文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天城愛娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加爾福．宗博伊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這位將擔任你的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一．多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必讓我一起 協助你們將這顆星球變得更加富饒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本機即將起飛駛向貝爾貝林的療養所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各位乘客再次確認安全帶是否繫好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經向對面傳達了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗博伊爾大人處理完事務明天就前去會談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕馬上就要讓諮詢會的各位退場了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對他們徹底失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然無法理解宗博伊爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓這個星球更加繁榮的用心良苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來應無人能再阻撓我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一刻終於要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪兒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我去找了找有沒有能用來做飯的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一會兒就能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一早出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再繼續了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再繼續前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順著這條河的東側支流走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能到靛藍花園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的對手是職業軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保護菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算因為這個死了 也是我自己的青任吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和多蒙沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護一個人 沒你想像的那麼容易
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大家也捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到這個份上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那麼想要那顆紅色石頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了…那麼無聊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親也是因為那東西死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了那種破石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人很容易就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再後悔也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我這麼說也沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙喜歡宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾喜歡大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天發生了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說已經有人盯上這個研究了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟計算的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玻爾維亞地區的宇宙飛來物質墜落的痕跡中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉夫特礦的濃度指數也和靛藍那裡的極為相似
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我的假設…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 剛才跟我說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說讓你留心一下自己周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是幫你沏茶的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都能喝到多蒙煮的美味咖啡 我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府也不是鐵板一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果出現了吉夫特礦的替代能源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會為此頭疼的人也大有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之 如果有狀況就打這個電話聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會立刻趕來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…路西法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須趕快通知多蒙他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信號是GO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再重複一便 信號是GO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果遇到妨礙 立刻排除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮壓後 盡可能回收背後相關人物的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始接觸物件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾就拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快退回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說連遺骸都沒留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兒子不在身邊算是不幸中的萬幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還在母親肚子裡的時候他父親就因故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能找到領養的人還好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼在這種地方哞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我還是不能放開菲莉雅不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這之後的路會更危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想把大家捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 要不要和我一起去深淵祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉和我一起保護菲莉雅 我們三個一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 沒想到你這麼珍視菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒了我宗吾就是個廢柴哞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然哞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會說話的怪石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和不感到奇怪 接受了怪石頭的怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個怪組台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於是時候告訴你了哞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是菲莉雅和莫拉的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片宇宙中 存在數不盡的生命哞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命們如蒲公英的絨毛紛飛流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們便是生命之種哞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之種…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,種子降落在適合誕生生命的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會成為星球的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孕育出創造生命的天使哞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在吉夫特星誕生的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換句話說 菲莉雅就是這個星球本身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而為了保護天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從同一顆種子誕生的守衛侍從就是莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是菲莉雅命中註定的僕從哞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每顆星球上 都有一位菲莉雅和一位莫拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開大地的菲莉雅消耗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不從祭壇補充
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會乾枯消散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…她知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是她的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望宗吾能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起保護好菲莉雅哞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們倆一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…通行證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找行政局有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借下用用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這速射時槍口向慣用手一邊動的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就叫你改了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼臉出現在我面前！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我知道的最棒的軍人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不是這個世界的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認識的一・多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在死在了那次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯這些屁話我會信嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的戰爭還沒有結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日淩晨 行政局諮詢會委員團搭乘的專機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在飛往貝爾貝林的途中失去了聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘員包括除宗博伊爾行政長官以外的諮詢會全員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在詳情尚未…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔的佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可靠的奧托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥氣的羅曼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定了嗎哞？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:17.06,edjp,,0,0,0,,めざめに思うのは　あたらしい朝のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:23.11,edjp,,0,0,0,,わたしはこの世界が好きなの　大好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:28.28,edjp,,0,0,0,,ひかりに呼ばれたら　裸足のままでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:31.41,edjp,,0,0,0,,向かいたくなる とめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.79,edjp,,0,0,0,,わたしもっともっと遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:39.88,edjp,,0,0,0,,ステップ踏みながらさがしてた それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:49.30,edjp,,0,0,0,,きっとね 「冒険にでるよ」 こころが夢みてる扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:53.26,edjp,,0,0,0,,今日が楽しくはじまる　レッツゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:56.52,edjp,,0,0,0,,追いかけてみたあの雲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.02,edjp,,0,0,0,,どっちへ逃げたのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.31,edjp,,0,0,0,,はやくつかまえなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:05.44,edjp,,0,0,0,,楽しさはじけて　レッツゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:08.70,edjp,,0,0,0,,追いかけてどこまでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.16,edjp,,0,0,0,,いっしょなら行けそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:13.24,edjp,,0,0,0,,となりにいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:17.58,edjp,,0,0,0,,もうこわくないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:17.06,edcn,,0,0,0,,在嶄新的清晨醒來 心中想的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:23.11,edcn,,0,0,0,,我喜歡這個世界 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:28.28,edcn,,0,0,0,,被光呼喚著 就算是光著腳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:31.41,edcn,,0,0,0,,也想要前去 不要攔著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.79,edcn,,0,0,0,,我要到更遠更遠的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:39.88,edcn,,0,0,0,,踏著步伐找尋著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:49.30,edcn,,0,0,0,,那一定是 「去冒險吧」 我心中夢寐以求的門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:53.26,edcn,,0,0,0,,今天開心地開始　Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:56.52,edcn,,0,0,0,,一直追著它看得雲朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.02,edcn,,0,0,0,,跑到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.31,edcn,,0,0,0,,要快點抓到它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:05.44,edcn,,0,0,0,,快樂綻放　Let's go！
